&lt;p&gt;NMI is seeking a Senior Database Administrator with MySQL experience who is passionate about running applications in an exceedingly high availability environment within our SRE organization.&amp;nbsp; This opportunity to work with similarly skilled professionals in a rapidly growing environment offers opportunities to level-up observability and automation skills while maintaining a series of databases across multiple key products.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
